verbose_text: Mutant proteins were expressed in the S. cerevisiae WB12 strain (aac2) for complementation studies, as this strain lacks functional ADP / ATP carriers, and in W303-1B strain (AAC2), which expresses one copy of AAC2 on the genome, to evaluate the dominance / recessivity of the aac2 Arg96His and aac2 Arg252Gly mutations.
